{"title":"鸢泽美咲","uid":"aa049cc12cfadeffe1d50ca50c6e8578","slug":"Galgame_Aokana_Misaki","date":"2026-02-24T15:00:00.000Z","updated":"2026-02-25T07:11:15.764Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Galgame_Aokana_Misaki.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<p>在美咲线的开头，有这么一句换引起了我的注意。我认为这句话有点哲理性就记了下来–&gt;<strong>那不是悲伤，也不是寂寥或者愤怒。是一种更加纠缠不清的心情，难以用语言明确表达。</strong><br>同样是美咲线的开头，美咲说了句「<strong>嗯······之前还是挺好玩的。怕你注意不到，我再和你强调一下，是过去</strong>」。因为刚刚玩过明日香线，回味这句话时，发现疑似是官方暗示？</p>\n<p>第六话，末尾。解释了“日向成为明日香眼里的女孩子的原因？” <strong>以前还玩空竞时，我头发留得很长，像个女孩子。</strong></p>\n<p>好……压抑啊。</p>\n<p>不是，我开始好奇：为什么美咲天然的给我一种“哦撒呐呐基米”（青梅）的感觉。日向和美咲在一开始就给我一种，他俩很熟的感觉。在明日香线之前，我甚至一直认为美咲才是青梅</p>\n<p>???不是，最终话？这就结束了？……不是，怎么还玩上过家家了</p>\n<p>我认为，这表白太突然。感觉像是，到时间了，直接开始。不过也有可能是我直接跳过了5话的“前置”</p>\n<p>我看不懂美咲线</p>\n","feature":false,"text":"[未完成的文章] 鸢泽美咲: 我有时候就是想飞，不飞一下的话整个人都感觉不对劲，只是这样而已...","permalink":"/post/Galgame_Aokana_Misaki","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":393,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"Galgame","slug":"Galgame","count":5,"path":"api/tags/Galgame.json"},{"name":"Aokana","slug":"Aokana","count":2,"path":"api/tags/Aokana.json"}],"toc":"","author":{"name":"MeowWow520","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://blogmeowwow520cn.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/hexo/source/img/MyHander.jpg","link":"https://blog.meowwow520.cn/","description":"Some says this place is where you can mine gold and diamonds! Everything I Want Wants Me Too.","socials":{}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{"title":"Ginka","uid":"467992fa0c493f3d28b2027d45016517","slug":"Galgame_Ginka","date":"2026-02-24T15:00:00.000Z","updated":"2026-02-25T06:48:15.774Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Galgame_Ginka.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"text":"[未完成的文章] ...","permalink":"/post/Galgame_Ginka","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":7,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"Galgame","slug":"Galgame","count":5,"path":"api/tags/Galgame.json"},{"name":"Ginka","slug":"Ginka","count":1,"path":"